OL,6,FTwo men have been jailed after posting
OL,7,Fracist messages on social media to
OL,8,Fstir up hatred after the Southport
OL,9,Fattack.
OL,11,FChristopher Taggart, 36, and Rhys
OL,12,FMcDonald, 34, called for protests
OL,13,Foutside a hotel in Runcorn where
OL,14,Fasylum seekers were staying.
OL,16,FThe pair, both from the Cheshire town,
OL,17,Fposted multiple messages on Facebook
OL,18,Fcontaining racial abuse and encouraged
OL,19,Fpeople to engage in racial hatred.
