OL,6,FCheshire Police became aware of
OL,7,Fmessages posted by the defendants
OL,8,Fbetween July 29 and 6 August, which
OL,9,Fwere openly available to view on the
OL,10,Fsocial media platform.
OL,12,FOfficers identified them from their
OL,13,Fonline profiles and, when Taggart's
OL,14,Fhome address was searched, they found
OL,15,Fa knuckle duster.
OL,17,FTaggart was jailed for 32 months and
OL,18,FMcDonald for 28 months after they both
OL,19,Fpleaded guilty to publishing written
OL,20,Fmaterial to stir up racial hatred.
