OL,6,FProsecutor Jane Morris told Chester
OL,7,FCrown Court: "The offending must be
OL,8,Fviewed in the context of the
OL,9,Fwidespread and extensively reported
OL,10,Fscenes of disorder, violence and
OL,11,Fcriminal damage which have taken place
OL,12,Faround the country ` beginning in
OL,13,FSouthport and spreading to other
OL,14,Flocations."
OL,16,FOn 30 July Taggart, of Caesars Close,
OL,17,Fposted: "Who's up for a rally?" and
OL,18,FMcDonald replied: "Need to march on
OL,19,Fthe Daresbury Hotel with torches and
OL,20,Fpitchforks. Enough is enough."
