OL,6,FMcDonald made no comment to police
OL,7,Fwhile Taggart claimed to have ADHD
OL,8,Fwhich caused impulsive actions and
OL,9,Fsaid he did not mean anything he
OL,10,Fposted.
OL,12,FMiss Morris said: "The police's
OL,13,Fpresence and patrols increased as a
OL,14,Fresult of the posts and these have
OL,15,Fremained in place.
OL,17,F"The offence is clearly aggravated by
OL,18,Fthe defendants' efforts to plan an
OL,19,Fevent designed to stir up hatred, as
OL,20,Fwell as by the timing of the incident
OL,21,Fand the sensitive social climate."
